# Navigation Icons Guidelines

## Core Principle

**ALL navigation links** in the header and footer components **MUST** be prefixed with an appropriate icon that reflects the link's label and purpose.

## Icon Library

Use **lucide-react** icons (as configured in the project's shadcn/ui setup).

```typescript
import { Settings, Home, CreditCard, LayoutDashboard, User, LogIn, LogOut, Menu, X } from 'lucide-react';
```

## Icon Selection by Label

Choose icons that semantically match the navigation label:

| Label/Purpose | Icon | Import |
|---------------|------|--------|
| Home / Accueil | `Home` | `lucide-react` |
| Dashboard / Tableau de bord | `LayoutDashboard` | `lucide-react` |
| Settings / Configuration / Paramètres | `Settings` | `lucide-react` |
| Credits / Crédits | `CreditCard` or `Coins` | `lucide-react` |
| Profile / Profil | `User` or `UserCircle` | `lucide-react` |
| Sign In / Connexion | `LogIn` | `lucide-react` |
| Sign Up / Inscription | `UserPlus` | `lucide-react` |
| Sign Out / Déconnexion | `LogOut` | `lucide-react` |
| About / À propos | `Info` | `lucide-react` |
| Contact | `Mail` or `MessageCircle` | `lucide-react` |
| Help / Aide | `HelpCircle` | `lucide-react` |
| Decks | `Layers` or `BookOpen` | `lucide-react` |
| Cards / Flashcards | `CreditCard` or `FileText` | `lucide-react` |
| Menu (mobile) | `Menu` | `lucide-react` |
| Close (mobile menu) | `X` | `lucide-react` |

