## Quick Reference

When adding a new navigation link:
1. Identify the label/purpose
2. Choose appropriate icon from lucide-react (refer to table above)
3. Import the icon component
4. Add icon before the text with `w-4 h-4 mr-2` classes
5. Ensure consistency across header, footer, and mobile menu
